# root-sandbox-sdk — Windsurf rules

Read AGENTS.md before generating any code. It is the single source of truth.

## Layer boundaries

| Layer | Files | Rule |
|---|---|---|
| UI layer | `app/`, `components/` | You may edit freely |
| Contract layer | `lib/branding.ts`, `lib/hooks/`, `app/actions/`, `lib/types/` | Read-only (except `branding.ts` for reskinning) |
| Core layer | `lib/root-api.ts`, `lib/redis.ts`, `lib/session.ts` | Never touch |

## Non-negotiable rules

- NEVER call `fetch('/api/...')` from a component — use hooks or server actions
- NEVER import `@root-credit/root-sdk` or `@/lib/root-api` in client components
- NEVER rename domain types (Payer, Payee, Payout, PaymentRail, etc.) — edit `lib/branding.ts` only
- NEVER store money in dollars — always integer cents (`Money` type)
- ALWAYS gate dashboard pages with `useSession()` → redirect to `/login`

## Installed shadcn/ui components

`Button`, `Card` / `CardHeader` / `CardTitle` / `CardDescription` / `CardContent` / `CardFooter`,
`Input`, `Label`, `Separator`,
`Table` / `TableHeader` / `TableBody` / `TableHead` / `TableRow` / `TableCell`,
`Badge` (variants: default secondary destructive outline success warning),
`Dialog` / `DialogContent` / `DialogHeader` / `DialogTitle` / `DialogTrigger` / `DialogDescription`,
`toast` (from `sonner`)

Do NOT add new npm packages or shadcn components.

## Reskinning

Edit only `lib/branding.ts`. All 14 keys must be updated. See `prompts/00-launch/PROMPT.md`
for the complete business definition template and per-page instructions.

## Verification

`pnpm typecheck` — zero errors required after every change.
